notamdrec.notam_text: E1428/25 NOTAMN Q) LIXX/QAFXX/IV/NBO/E /000/188/4119N01321E999 A) LIBB LIMM LIRR PART 1 OF 2 B) 2506131727 C) PERM E) FIREFIGHTING ACTIVITY IS REGULATED AS FLW: -AIRCRAFT NOT INVOLVED IN FIREFIGHTING OPERATIONS MUST NOT FLY OVER THE FIRE AREA AND MUST EXERCISE EXTREME CAUTION WHEN FLYING NEAR IT, CONSIDERING THE POSSIBLE INTERVENTION OF FIREFIGHTING ACFT. THEREFORE, WHEN AN AERIAL FIREFIGHTING OPERATION IS ANNOUNCED/ACTIVE, IT IS PROHIBITED TO FLY IN THE ZONES IDENTIFIED BY THE FIRE-FIGHTING AUTHORITIES AND NOTIFIED BY THE COMPETENT AUTHORITY OR, IN THE ABSENCE OF SPECIFIC PROVISIONS: I. WITHIN CONTROLLED AIRSPACE, IN THE ABSENCE OF SPECIFIC COMMUNICATIONS ABOUT THE AREA AFFECTED BY THE FIREFIGHTING OPERATIONS FROM THE ENGAGED ACFT, BELOW 760M (2500FT) AGL WITHIN AN AREA EXTENDING UP TO A HORIZONTAL DISTANCE OF 4KM (2 NM) FROM THE FIRE II. OUTSIDE CONTROLLED AIRSPACE, BELOW 900M (3000FT) AGL, WITHIN AN AREA EXTENDING UP TO A HORIZONTAL DISTANCE OF 9KM (5NM) FROM THE FIRE. -TIMELY UPDATES REGARDING THE ZONES AND AREAS AFFECTED CAN BE BROADCAST ON GROUND/AIR/GROUND FREQUENCIES. PART 1 OF 2 E1428/25 NOTAMN Q) LIXX/QAFXX/IV/NBO/E /000/188/4119N01321E999 A) LIBB LIMM LIRR PART 2 OF 2 B) 2506131727 C) PERM E) -THE ENGAGED FIREFIGHTING AIRCRAFT KEEP THE ATS UNIT RESPONSIBLE FOR THE AFFECTED AREA INFORMED ABOUT THE FIREFIGHTING OPERATIONS AND THEIR CONCLUSION. -THE ATS UNIT RESPONSIBLE FOR THE AREA AFFECTED BY THE FIREFIGHTING OPERATIONS PROVIDES AIR TRAFFIC SERVICES, AS FAR AS POSSIBLE: 1.TO THE AIRCRAFT ENGAGED IN FIREFIGHTING OPERATIONS, EXCEPT IN THE FIREFIGHTING AREA WHERE IT PROVIDES ONLY FLIGHT INFORMATION AND ALERT SERVICES. RMK: IF A CTR IS AFFECTED BY THE FIRE, SID/STAR/INSTR APCH PROC COULD BE TEMPORARILY SUSPENDED OR MODIFIED 2.TO OTHER GAT FLIGHTS, BASED ON THE INFORMATION AVAILABLE REGARDING THE FIREFIGHTING ACTIVITY, WHICH MAY STILL BE INCOMPLETE. REF AIP ENR 1.1.1.4 'POLICE, CUSTOMS AND PATROL FLIGHTS ENGAGED IN URGENCY MISSIONS', PARAGRAPH C 'FIREFIGHTING' PART 2 OF 2

notamdrec.notam_text: E1428/25 NOTAMN Q) LIXX/QAFXX/IV/NBO/E /000/188/4119N01321E999 A) LIBB LIMM LIRR PART 1 OF 2 B) 2506131727 C) PERM E) FIREFIGHTING ACTIVITY IS REGULATED AS FLW: -AIRCRAFT NOT INVOLVED IN FIREFIGHTING OPERATIONS MUST NOT FLY OVER THE FIRE AREA AND MUST EXERCISE EXTREME CAUTION WHEN FLYING NEAR IT, CONSIDERING THE POSSIBLE INTERVENTION OF FIREFIGHTING ACFT. THEREFORE, WHEN AN AERIAL FIREFIGHTING OPERATION IS ANNOUNCED/ACTIVE, IT IS PROHIBITED TO FLY IN THE ZONES IDENTIFIED BY THE FIRE-FIGHTING AUTHORITIES AND NOTIFIED BY THE COMPETENT AUTHORITY OR, IN THE ABSENCE OF SPECIFIC PROVISIONS: I. WITHIN CONTROLLED AIRSPACE, IN THE ABSENCE OF SPECIFIC COMMUNICATIONS ABOUT THE AREA AFFECTED BY THE FIREFIGHTING OPERATIONS FROM THE ENGAGED ACFT, BELOW 760M (2500FT) AGL WITHIN AN AREA EXTENDING UP TO A HORIZONTAL DISTANCE OF 4KM (2 NM) FROM THE FIRE II. OUTSIDE CONTROLLED AIRSPACE, BELOW 900M (3000FT) AGL, WITHIN AN AREA EXTENDING UP TO A HORIZONTAL DISTANCE OF 9KM (5NM) FROM THE FIRE. -TIMELY UPDATES REGARDING THE ZONES AND AREAS AFFECTED CAN BE BROADCAST ON GROUND/AIR/GROUND FREQUENCIES. PART 1 OF 2 E1428/25 NOTAMN Q) LIXX/QAFXX/IV/NBO/E /000/188/4119N01321E999 A) LIBB LIMM LIRR PART 2 OF 2 B) 2506131727 C) PERM E) -THE ENGAGED FIREFIGHTING AIRCRAFT KEEP THE ATS UNIT RESPONSIBLE FOR THE AFFECTED AREA INFORMED ABOUT THE FIREFIGHTING OPERATIONS AND THEIR CONCLUSION. -THE ATS UNIT RESPONSIBLE FOR THE AREA AFFECTED BY THE FIREFIGHTING OPERATIONS PROVIDES AIR TRAFFIC SERVICES, AS FAR AS POSSIBLE: 1.TO THE AIRCRAFT ENGAGED IN FIREFIGHTING OPERATIONS, EXCEPT IN THE FIREFIGHTING AREA WHERE IT PROVIDES ONLY FLIGHT INFORMATION AND ALERT SERVICES. RMK: IF A CTR IS AFFECTED BY THE FIRE, SID/STAR/INSTR APCH PROC COULD BE TEMPORARILY SUSPENDED OR MODIFIED 2.TO OTHER GAT FLIGHTS, BASED ON THE INFORMATION AVAILABLE REGARDING THE FIREFIGHTING ACTIVITY, WHICH MAY STILL BE INCOMPLETE. REF AIP ENR 1.1.1.4 'POLICE, CUSTOMS AND PATROL FLIGHTS ENGAGED IN URGENCY MISSIONS', PARAGRAPH C 'FIREFIGHTING' PART 2 OF 2
